## SERP ANALYSIS

### Competitor Summary

**Common H2 topics competitors cover (baseline — do not copy):**
- Classic French manicure for wedding guests
- Neutral and nude nail ideas
- Milky white and glazed finishes
- Chrome and shimmer options
- Pastel shades for spring/summer
- Bold colour options (red, burgundy, deep jewel tones)
- Garden wedding nails
- Black-tie wedding nails
